{"tid":2137111,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"目光問題爭執     3越漢闖元朗逢吉鄉士多斬傷3人逃逸","createTime":"2020-08-02T15:55:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T16:41:37.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f95cf5927edeb8d8d52f24b73e33f8b2c90a4499","tid":2137111,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T15:55:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/目光問題爭執-3越漢闖逢吉鄉士多斬傷3人逃逸-135747007.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E7%9B%AE%E5%85%89%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%E7%88%AD%E5%9F%B7-3%E8%B6%8A%E6%BC%A2%E9%97%96%E9%80%A2%E5%90%89%E9%84%89%E5%A3%AB%E5%A4%9A%E6%96%AC%E5%82%B73%E4%BA%BA%E9%80%83%E9%80%B8-135747007.html&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2F0PYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=3585443c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/目光問題爭執-3越漢闖逢吉鄉士多斬傷3人逃逸-135747007.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Uo2pvhCo2FSc2BzayNLDRQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/onccinstantnews.com/c9accea249ec3a0911b4fa2a5b13814f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FUo2pvhCo2FSc2BzayNLDRQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2Fc9accea249ec3a0911b4fa2a5b13814f&h=6a351641&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2F0PYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=d3248558\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】元朗逢吉鄉發生斬人案！今日(2日)晚上9時許，警方接獲一名女子報案，指突然有3名持刀越南漢衝入元朗逢吉鄉路一間士多，將其3名男子斬傷，兇徒事後四散逃去。<br />\n<br />\n警方人員接報趕至，於現場發現3名男子倒臥血泊中，當中一人腹部中刀腸臟外露，其餘兩人分別臉部及手部中刀，救護員到場替傷者包紮後立即將各人送院急救。現場士多內外留下斑斑血漬及玻璃樽，懷疑與案有關。警方在附近兜截後拘捕一名男子，並將案件列作傷人案處理，正追緝3名在逃男子歸案。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，5名本地男女事發前正於士多內消遣，其中一人先外出取車，期間與3名於附近友人家中消遣的越南漢疑因目光問題發生爭執，其後各自離開。未幾，該3名越南漢便持刀折返並闖入士多向眾人施襲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/FA8upX9d3LkGaTTa35GFLg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/onccinstantnews.com/b6fc96016eb9450bb03ffd246c338761\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FFA8upX9d3LkGaTTa35GFLg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2Fb6fc96016eb9450bb03ffd246c338761&h=354f9605&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4ac902f9fa8a957c2ea89c43fd97aedbfd26b7a2","tid":2137111,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T15:56:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b615a7c4d059a856789df02bac4d49de28d67dc9","tid":2137111,"uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T15:57:16.000Z","msg":"越南仔  VS  元朗鄉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5926bc02ad767d245c98d66249b161cb48473b10","tid":2137111,"uid":33939,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T15:57:46.000Z","msg":"越南幫3:0元朗鄉黑<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c0737a599ab1bd19c1ac3d2f19b382551e61bf8","tid":2137111,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T15:58:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解近排咁多同類案件，越來越猖狂"},{"pid":"3c9e13722cf2d7c43f08bec098a55e0ed8b58e5c","tid":2137111,"uid":58316,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T15:58:22.000Z","msg":"佢北越既"},{"pid":"f29c1de79e0b7f1af8fa257f2bc5918569ed42dc","tid":2137111,"uid":117580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T15:58:42.000Z","msg":"流浮山刀手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1573e1e1eb528fe6e8f4dc2c0ca6619c9878afae","tid":2137111,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3c9e